{# Tips #}
<section class="py-16 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-900/50">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
    <h2 class="section-heading text-center mb-12">Tips for Visa Applications</h2>
    <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
      <div class="card p-6">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-brand-100 dark:bg-brand-900/30 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
            <i data-lucide="file-text" class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-600 dark:text-brand-400"></i>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-1">Prepare Documents Early</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Gather degree certificates, transcripts, work experience letters, and passport copies well in advance. Many documents need apostille or notarization.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card p-6">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-green-100 dark:bg-green-900/30 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
            <i data-lucide="languages" class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 dark:text-green-400"></i>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-1">Take Language Tests Early</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">IELTS, TOEFL, or other language tests often have limited availability. Book your test early and allow time for retakes if needed.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card p-6">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-purple-100 dark:bg-purple-900/30 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
            <i data-lucide="scale" class="w-5 h-5 text-purple-600 dark:text-purple-400"></i>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-1">Understand Legal Requirements</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Each country has specific requirements. Research salary thresholds, health insurance mandates, and financial proof requirements for your target country.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card p-6">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-yellow-100 dark:bg-yellow-900/30 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
            <i data-lucide="users" class="w-5 h-5 text-yellow-600 dark:text-yellow-400"></i>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-1">Leverage Your Employer</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Many companies have immigration teams or work with specialized lawyers. Don't hesitate to ask your employer for guidance throughout the visa process.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

